                  <decoDesc>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d01"><locus target="#11r"/><desc>A miniature of <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1024MosesLaw"></ref> with caption <foreign xml:lang ="gez">ነብዩ፡ ሙሴ፡ ምስለ፡ ፅላት፡</foreign></desc><note>The catalogue has 'Saint with a book' but the caption makes it clear that it is Moses with the Tablets of the Law</note></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d02"><locus target="#41r"/><desc>Breaking the Bread at the Last Supper, <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1067LastSupper"></ref> with caption <foreign xml:lang ="gez">ምሥተ፡ ሐሙስ።</foreign></desc></decoNote>
